{"tid":116663,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打有婦科中醫介紹？想睇卵巢多囊症","createTime":"2017-02-11T14:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T07:58:29.000Z","uid":44731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9bda327212d009e813c9a23b3f7162d35750b7d1","tid":116663,"uid":44731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T14:48:13.000Z","msg":"上年十月去睇西醫，確診有卵巢多囊症，<br />\n但西醫話唔算嚴重，冇開藥，等七月覆診，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係叫我控制體重，做運動，改善生活習慣之類。<br />\n後來我上網睇話中醫可以調理身體，對個病會有改善，<br />\n想問下有冇有喱個病既絲打有婦科中醫介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該！"},{"pid":"7073fd41c2c62eb387b45a198793d1207969d007","tid":116663,"uid":146880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T07:58:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/joinchat/F_YAwxFmiPsz-9cLRebRgQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FF_YAwxFmiPsz-9cLRebRgQ&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTSxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=fda50f9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/joinchat/F_YAwxFmiPsz-9cLRebRgQ</a><br />\n入黎傾，剛開的"}]}